{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 53,
  "title": "第五十三章（盜竽）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "使我挈有知也。行於大道，唯施是畏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "大道甚夷，民甚好解。朝甚除，田甚蕪，倉甚虛，服文采，帶利劍，厭食而齎財有餘，是謂盜竽，非道也。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "介，大也。老子疾時王不行大道，故設此言。使我介然有知於政事，我則行於大道，躬行無為之化。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯，獨也。獨畏有所施為，恐失道意。欲賞善，恐偽善生；欲信忠，恐詐忠起。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夷，平易也。徑，邪、不平正也。大道甚平易，而民好從邪徑也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "高台榭，宮室修。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 4,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "農事廢，不耕治。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "五穀傷害，國無儲也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 47,
          "end": 47
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "好飾偽，貴外華。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "尚剛強，武且奢。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 47,
          "end": 47
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "多嗜欲，無足時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 47,
          "end": 47
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓而君有餘者，是由劫盜以為服飾，持行誇人，不知身死家破，親戚並隨也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 35,
          "end": 36
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人君所行如是，此非道也。復言也哉者，痛傷之辭。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言若使我可介然有知，行大道於天下，唯施為之是畏也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言大道蕩然正平，而民猶尚舍之而不由，好從邪徑，況復施為以塞大道之中乎。故曰，大道甚夷，而民好徑。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "朝，宮室也。除，潔好也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 4,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "朝甚除，則田甚蕪，倉甚虛，設一而眾害生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 47,
          "end": 47
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "凡物不以其道得之，則皆邪也，邪則盜也。夸而不以其道得之，竊位也，故舉非道以明非道，則皆盜夸也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
